id":"43a79ae42f18284c864d7be30247f41194628615","tid":1543970,"uid":39855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b25d1963b1e213fc1bb485c155a30d1807f5737","tid":1543970,"uid":140552,"like":203,"dislike":1,"score":202,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:35:09.000Z","msg":"福建幫定元朗鄉黑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:56:53.000Z","msg":"同上"},{"pid":"b599e930ed885695fad8f4cad39a1cd5de0fcf36","tid":1543970,"uid":76470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:00:08.000Z","msg":"多謝芬姐為前線出心出力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />識到勇武都唔割同唔督灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知芬姐有無出錢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b07d81062719fe1f062ffa51b6334b0d685027","tid":1543970,"uid":21899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:00:26.000Z","msg":"Regina: 隱形、精密、非常犀利既幕後大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a9762fdd68fdc5457ed35bc7ce8b60e6f10f56","tid":1543970,"uid":293896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:01:48.000Z","msg":"831 死左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0582ba3023d33c6281367703f7a23d6d5af0609e","tid":1543970,"uid":51723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:10:34.000Z","msg":"哦 佢撐暴徒 等佢無晒藍絲啲票啦"},{"pid":"029c3d02477bc6d6f86d54a7d16cf7d1766bc497","tid":1543970,"uid":279895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美芬義士"},{"pid":"8021dff176989ddaa883da5fe74f3169f3f2e32e","tid":1543970,"uid":154429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:39:14.000Z","msg":"咁快d拉左芬芬佢啦，知情不報，包庇勇武。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1925511bb694f45a9b496e8c8713879b0cbf9c","tid":1543970,"uid":120084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:40:17.000Z","msg":"發夢鼠王芬仲有一齊上過前線啦"},{"pid":"526b8ba46d448609bc1843ea5e228db7cf637a92","tid":1543970,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a5d5f4c53bfedb9780c1fb6211bf2f03e03b63","tid":1543970,"uid":3564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:41:53.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借少少位文宣一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n907 機場攻略(更新版)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1ZdOQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1ZdOQY.jpg&h=73c39421&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7s8mXKj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7s8mXKj.jpg&h=a2d13636&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T4vMppk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT4vMppk.jpg&h=f119fdbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1) 步兵測試方法<br />\n- 和理非，**普通市民/旅客身份**<br />\n- 市民/旅客裝，唔着黑色衫，唔叫口號<br />\n- **可以戴普通口罩**，唔需要其他裝備 (帶左要有心理準備隨時需要棄裝)<br />\n- 地點: 同上次一樣，**暢達路巴士總站**，另一個選擇係**暢航路**<br />\n- 策略: 到左巴士總站唔一定要企定等，**緊記市民/旅客身份，可以係周圍行行企企，排下隊，落車上車**<br />\n- 如果有部份人真係怕係機場島走唔到，搭巴士入機場然後上返車，**係青馬收費廣場同機場之間不停來回**<br />\n- 優先搭巴士入，建議大家首先**集合左係青馬收費廣場**再搭巴士入機場<br />\n- **青馬收費廣場係交通樽頸，如果所有途徑巴士都埋站會好影響交通**<br />\n- 如果想搭機場快線，建議集中係青衣站，集合到一大班人可以一齊入閘<br />\n<br />\n關於清場/逃走路線<br />\n- **無時無刻緊記自己普通市民/旅客身份**，只要**有合理原因係機場範圍出現**就唔需要怕警察，上次 901 普通市民/旅客都只係企係機場島其他地方等，就算今次有咩突發事情警察決定清場都唔需要好似上次咁逃走<br />\n- 有咩合理原因可以係機場範圍出現？<br />\n接機/送機，參觀機場，巴士/地鐵愛好者，即興旅行，參觀航空探知館等等，可以參考100個理由玩轉香港機場全攻略<br />\n- **無論如何都唔好係 T1/2 機場客運大樓附近設路障塞路**，即使有任何行動都一定要**等到三點**後全部人入左機場先<br />\n- 如果有人帶頭衝入 T1，而令到路面情況好混亂所以好多人被迫入左 T1 混入其他遊客當中，大家要緊記身份，千祈唔好係入面示威或者遊蕩違反禁制令<br />\n- 萬一警察真係清場，記得**緊貼其他遊客，佢地去邊大家就去邊**，普通市民/旅客冇犯法係唔需要逃走<br />\n- 如果警察唔容許任何人企係巴士總站，可以**去附近其他戰略性位置(例如暢航路)等到有返巴士搭**，試問冇任何交通工具旅客又點進出機場？<br />\n<br />\n- 以防萬一，會盡快提供機場島，東涌，青馬收費廣場同埋青衣嘅詳細地圖，當中包括戰略性位置，所有交通路線，廁所等等<br />\n- **密切留意睇Telegram頻道**，當日會安排 Bot 俾前線測試員報料<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2) 車隊測試方法<br />\n- **兩點經過青馬收費廣場**開往機場幫手測試，帶多張$500找續<br />\n唔需要離開機場島，隨時準備萬一有需要時接仔女放學，建議到時可以係一號停車場附近等"},{"pid":"1ce9e96e3e1a37e0f96318db814969cf285546da","tid":1543970,"uid":308850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:42:38.000Z","msg":"老鼠芬 你對唔對得著班藍絲 對你好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64204849641bd176cb6cd4362ce003b893996861","tid":1543970,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n👉🏻<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>中英聯合聲明的謬誤</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n若果一件物件是從來未曾擁有過，拿到手上是談不上「恢復」及「收回」的。同樣道理，1997年前中華人民共和國從來未曾對香港行使過主權，如何談得上「恢復行使主權」？中華人民共和國的漢族（即「中國人民」）從來也沒有擁有過香港，試問又如何「收回」香港？<br />\n<br />\n因此，中華人民共和國取得香港的土地應該形容為「兼併」或「呑併」。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n👉🏻<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>不平等條約無效論是謊言</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如兩國以和平條約（Peace Treaty）終止戰爭，而某些領土由一國割讓予另一國，則在國際法中亦被視為透過割讓（Cession）而取得主權。過去的國際法觀點認為，以戰爭解決國與國之間的爭議屬國家的權利，而「和平條約」的作用是令交戰雙方以某些條款（包括部份領土的轉讓）為代價以終止戰爭。因此，按照「時空性原則」，1842年及1860年割讓香港島及九龍半島均符合當時的國際法。<br />\n<br />\n國際法中，領土的轉讓只有是否合法，而沒有平等不平等。<br />\n<br />\n在中華人民共和國成為國家之前，英國已經從清帝國手中符合國際法地取得香港的主權。另一方面，中華人民共和國亦從來沒有繼承過清帝國的仼何權益。因此，《中英聯合聲明》中所謂「對香港恢復行使主權」的「恢復」根本無從談起，並且只是一個猜想。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cbwr6sW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCbwr6sW.png&h=7ee87500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPAHEN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPAHEN9.png&h=e166e8fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n知情不報者 你地都係半個兇手！<br />\n你唯一可以做就係站出黎 講個真相比全香港市民聽！ ！ 還死者一個清白！</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肛犬：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n別再喱係電視後面，敢就走出黎攞出CCTV之類証據黎証明831冇人死冇人重傷囉仆街共狗！！！</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/05/104231_3a6ab00f3ec1c5387f321c23ffcf1893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2F104231_3a6ab00f3ec1c5387f321c23ffcf1893.jpg&h=7d68f7dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必問：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾倍OT收，係咪仲要&quot;好合理要屌埋女示者&quot;咁辛苦？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民主訴求，缺一不可；<br />\n<br />\n以眼還眼，鷹犬全鎖；<br />\n<br />\n有錯企定，即決勿拖！<br />\n<br />\n民主斬件，仲當我傻！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，未贏收科？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span></span></span></span><br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除非你係個班那埋護照旁身嘅扮民霸權，永續利益獨賣囉！！！</span></span></span></span></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"287b1cf8498ec205b341b5ad072b641368b13974","tid":1543970,"uid":190181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:43:41.000Z","msg":"831 CCTV<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n906 遮打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n907 機場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n908 美領 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596b63b23b9677f05935ea7028fc891f596164a9","tid":1543970,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b25d1963b1e213fc1bb485c155a30d1807f5737","tid":1543970,"uid":140552,"like":203,"dislike":1,"score":202,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:35:09.000Z","msg":"福建幫定元朗鄉黑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:43:52.000Z","msg":"華生！！！"},{"pid":"98ae2db7c8ccb878791bdd2e6d8629be0a7f7549","tid":1543970,"uid":198290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:53:51.000Z","msg":"佢識含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36f564d12560d851d58093244cadfdac119dbf4","tid":1543970,"uid":264081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b25d1963b1e213fc1bb485c155a30d1807f5737","tid":1543970,"uid":140552,"like":203,"dislike":1,"score":202,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:35:09.000Z","msg":"福建幫定元朗鄉黑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09